main event: Two lights were observed in the sky, one approximately 3 feet behind the other, disappearing over the horizon in the east.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 1 minute 30 seconds, The lights were the size of a half dollar, Observers noted that there were white lights on top of each one, The lights were possibly the right wing tip lights of aircraft, Witnesses were two civilians aged 19 and 15 from Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
sighted object: two white lights in the sky
witness description: civilians, ages 19 and 15, from Milwaukee, Wisconsin
